dreisoft.tresos.tresosdb.api.model.v1.swcomponenttemplate.swcinternalbehavior.servicemapping

Interface IRoleBasedRPortAssignment

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IEntity

    public interface IRoleBasedRPortAssignment
extends IEntity
    IRoleBasedRPortAssignment: Entity class of the tresosDB model.

    This class specifies an assignment of a role to a particular R-Port. This port must contain a service which is outside of the component and called by the component in order to handle a particular issue (e.g. a communication event).

    GENERATED CODE. DO NOT CHANGE!
